Installation of OpenCV on RPi 2:
Cf. https://singleboardblog.com/install-python-opencv-on-raspberry-pi/
$ sudo apt update
$ pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel
$ sudo apt-get install -y libhdf5-dev libhdf5-serial-dev python3-pyqt5 libatlas-base-dev libjasper-dev
$ pip install --no-cache-dir opencv-contrib-python==4.5.3.56

To launch start_gunicorn.sh on startup:
$ sudo nano /etc/rc.local
/home/sebastien/projects/usb_camera_stream/start_gunicorn.sh &